ts/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:21:53.000Z","msg":"龍門唔係退出左黃圈?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:25:20.000Z","msg":"同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d3a9c252c83312eb3f53a54454d13a20869ad2","tid":2460791,"uid":59919,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:25:33.000Z","msg":"理性啲講<br />\n無咁大個頭唔好戴咁大頂帽<br />\n之前仲逆市開分店"},{"pid":"b08c28e8506a5e02a88a8d8dbed43ba4277a77ab","tid":2460791,"uid":377811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a9016c52c1eca3b79069ab448ce27c0d5879850a","tid":2460791,"uid":261873,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"02e1c3c00af6458bc2e8f514a44d9d0a16b63dfd","tid":2460791,"uid":309023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:09:39.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈咁勁都搞成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:21:53.000Z","msg":"龍門唔係退出左黃圈?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:40:30.000Z","msg":"嗰陣國安法個個都驚到閪咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢見人哋眾志又解散 又退埋一份<br />\n<br />\n如果係呢個位我唔會怪佢<br />\n畢竟有咩事嘅又唔係我哋幫佢孭飛<br />\n佢嗰陣都係出名嗰咋"},{"pid":"8f3f64a2cceac7067711dcf61755f8729b0a967c","tid":2460791,"uid":205676,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:59:08.000Z","msg":"個人認為主要錯在餐廳經營不善 佢開咁多間分店 但每一間我都唔敢話質素好好 以銅鑼灣為例 無論佢服務、環境同食物都好唔理想 食物質素方面 佢好努力改善 但感覺都喺徒勞無功 食物選擇愈嚟愈多 但冇邊樣野喺會想食完再食 欠缺一款皇牌食物我覺得喺致命傷 人手方面仲大問題 啲啊姐真喺好hea"},{"pid":"6415a033003ef6c04c1d4498a334d90a7eb3ac11","tid":2460791,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4b9c0fbc0272d04b69387f0a678d9f2b516a19e8","tid":2460791,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:05:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YH4ZE7x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYH4ZE7x.jpg&h=fb25a1c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今朝有嚟食早餐嘅客人可能會知道...<br />\n執達吏到咗尖沙咀店...<br />\n可能7日後就係瓏門嘅最後一日...<br />\n<br />\n瓏門無論做咩都會被評論<br />\n我一直以為清者自清<br />\n與其花時間去內鬥<br />\n不如做好食物出品<br />\n<br />\n生意受謠言影響每況越下<br />\n加上疫情、停晚市堂食<br />\n相信飲食業內都無一倖免<br />\n<br />\n我冇能力改變香港<br />\n只希望可以為運動付出嘅年青人做一D嘢<br />\n所以我喺餐廳生意最好嘅時候去咗攪資源中心<br />\n<br />\n我承認我係喺運動中最失敗的生意人<br />\n直至宜家不但冇車冇樓銀行冇錢<br />\n甚至連一班伙記生計都可能維持唔到<br />\n<br />\n多謝各位一直支持<br />\n無論7日後瓏門存在與否<br />\n我永遠都會記得同大家行過呢一段路<br />\n亦希望大家記得瓏門改好咗嘅味道<br />\n<br />\n對唔住思緒好混亂<br />\n張俊傑（2021年4月1日減7日）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T06:00:30.000Z","msg":"收得人貴但係啲嘢難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91fd55fc129d7635fba805d567805e96fade86e5","tid":2460791,"uid":195248,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"979d5ea5ef9648ec301f5aabfbfd5aa2cdaa4e13","tid":2460791,"uid":261505,"like":20,"dislike":3,"score":17,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:07:03.000Z","msg":"Supply and demand<br />\n難食就無人食<br />\nCCtoy得網上支持 實際上就唔去幫襯"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T07:18:55.000Z","msg":"五毛黎講你都算幾勤力<br />\n起晒你底開咁撚多po都未block<br />\n走甩左你唔好意思<br />\nblock返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ed7e78212d2d4a5f2e0d76c85a0bfe2358f326","tid":2460791,"uid":261505,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"13c3f86109c770cbc6d1f7f0a86e6028155692b2","tid":2460791,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"979d5ea5ef9648ec301f5aabfbfd5aa2cdaa4e13","tid":2460791,"uid":261505,"like":20,"dislike":3,"score":17,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:07:03.000Z","msg":"Supply a